<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org2b8e7a5">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li><p>
Create a website with a  <code>class red</code> div which has a <code>backgrond cloro of red</code> and <code>color white</code>.
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-css"><span style="color: #6c3163; font-weight: bold;">.red</span>{
    <span style="color: #3a81c3; font-weight: bold;">background-color</span>: <span style="color: #ffffff; background-color: #ff0000;">red</span>;
    <span style="color: #3a81c3; font-weight: bold;">color</span>:<span style="color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff;">white</span>; 
}
<span style="color: #6c3163; font-weight: bold;">.blue</span>{
    <span style="color: #3a81c3; font-weight: bold;">color</span>: <span style="color: #ffffff; background-color: #0000ff;">blue</span>;
}
</pre>
</div></li>

